	/// Full Adaptation activities narrative, 1:1 translation of Tableau's ws.adaptation title_text template: paragraph 1 built from Name/Adapt Plan/Eu Com ('{Name} {Adapt Plan} an adaptation plan (n). It {Eu Com} a signatory...'), blank-line separator, then paragraph 2 (the existing 'Adaptation Text' EU-projects sentence, itself blank when no Initiative is recorded).
